types.name: satellite_channel_prefix
types.doc:
Puppet will access our Satellite instance and ensure that a set of channels exists for the
          given prefix and that this host is subscribed to them.

properties.name: ensure
properties.doc: The prefix of the channel label that this machine should be subscribed to.  The current base channel label is rhel-x86_64-server-6.  Values can match `/.*/`.

parameters.name: name
parameters.doc: An arbitrary tag for your own reference; the name of the message.

providers.name: satellite
providers.doc:
Provides Subversion support for the repo type

Supported features: `versionable`.
